Thu May  5 15:58:49 PDT 1988	chessin@political
We need a monitor command to toggle the flags for the serial ports,
since we don't have a config file for them.  (The flag indicates
whether open should wait for carrier detect or not.  It is usually used
when you have hard-wired terminals with 3-wire (TXD, RXD, and ground)
cables.)
